>								<li>									In <a href="2">Part 2</a>,									Goran tracks down Keius and finds he has become a powerful superbeing, who then saves Goran from attacking rebels before surrendering to them.									<ol>										<li>											In <a href="2/1">Episode 1</a>,											Goran searches for Keius and finds him hiding on another remote world, after having become some kind of immortal superbeing thanks to his miraculous breakthrough.										</li>										<li>											In <a href="2/2">Episode 2</a>,											Keius explains to Goran his plan to use his new powers to stop the galactic civil war, and quietly takes his first steps in doing so with Goran.										</li>										<li>											In <a href="2/3">Episode 3</a>,											a rebel warship attacks Keius and Goran as they depart that remote world, and Keius blatantly allows himself to be captured to facilitate Goran's escape.										</li>									</ol>								</li>								<li>									In <a href="3">Part 3</a>,									Keius searches for the origins of his nanotechnological superpowers, after using them to quell the civil war that threatened his civilization.									<ol>										<li>											In <a href="3/1">Episode 1</a>,											Keius is freed from prison as the civil war ends thanks to his subtle telepathic manipulations, and he begins his quest for the origins of those powers.										</li>										<li>											In <a href="3/2">Episode 2</a>,											Keius and Tatia grow romantically closer as she accompanies him on the next leg of his quest to trace the origins of his new powers.										</li>										<li>											In <a href="3/3">Episode 3</a>,											Keius embarks on the final leg of his quest for the origin of his powers, discovering their extragalactic origins despite some opposition he meets on the way.										</li>									</ol>								</li>							</ol>						</li>					</ol>				</section><? require $_SERVER['DOCUMENT_ROOT'] . "